QuestData.Title: Nesingwary's Trek
QuestData.Description: De greatest hunter from your lands, de dwarf Nesingwary, has come to participate in de Great Hunt.$b$bIf you are enough of a hunter to join him, den travel to de Nesingwary Trek along de northeastern region of Zuldazar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Hemet Nesingwary at Nesingwary's Trek.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Hemet Nesingwary at Nesingwary's Trek.
